query:
SELECT
                file_id AS "file_id!",
                cell_id AS "cell_id!",
                pile_id AS "pile_id!",
                files_per_cell AS "files_per_cell!",
                pile_hostname AS "pile_hostname!",
                pile_path AS "pile_path!"
            FROM stash.storage_fofs_view
            JOIN stash.files ON files.id = file_id
            WHERE pile_hostname = $1 AND b3sum IS NULL
